                    <p>EZYFEST is built on a Bootstrap framework which means your site will be accessible, and look cool on all screen sizes, a must have feature in the current digital climate. EZYFEST provides you with a slick, modern, cost saving, responsive design to showcase your festival to the world!</p>
                </div>
