                <div class="info">
                    <h4 class="text-center white-class">Plugins</h4>
                    <p>Simply select from the range of plugins to build your webpage. EZYFEST has all your festival website needs!</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-6 col-md-6 col-lg-6 marg">
